<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἡρακλάμμων Καλλίστῳ τῶι 

    <lb n="2"/>τιμιωτάτῳ τέκνῳ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἤδη σοι καὶ ἄλλας ἐπιστολὰς ἔπεμψα 

    <lb n="4"/><hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>κανὰς καὶ σύ μοι οὐκέτι ἀντέγραψας. 

    <lb n="5"/>καλῶς οὖν ποήσεις <del rend="erasure">καλωσουνπ</del> ὁπόταν 

    <lb n="6"/>πληρώσῃς τὴν συνγραφὴν ἢ <add place="supralinear">ὡ</add>ς δήποτε 

    <lb n="7"/>γενέσθαι πρὸς ἐμὲ καθώς μοι ἔγραψας. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἡγοῦμαι γὰρ ὅτι ἄμεινον ἡμᾶς ἀνέχε-

    <lb n="9"/>σθαι ἀλλήλων ἢ ξένων ὡς καὶ πρότερον 

    <lb n="10"/>ἔγραψά σοι περὶ παιδίων ἐὰν που ἐπινοῇς. 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ γὰρ ἡ <choice><corr>γραῖα</corr><sic>γρεα</sic></choice> ἔπεμψέ μοι ἀπὸ Ἀλεξαν-

    <lb n="12"/>δρείας ὅτι ἂν σχῇς Κάλ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λισ</unclear>τον ἔχεις 

    <lb n="13"/>τὰ παιδία. ἐὰν δὲ παραγέ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νῃ</supplied> οὐδὲν ἔσται 

    <lb n="14"/>μέσον ἡμῶν τὸ δυνάμεν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ον</supplied> ἐμὲ ἢ σὲ λυ-

    <lb n="15"/>πῆσαι. ἐφρόντισα δὲ καὶ ν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>νίσκων 

    <lb n="16"/>πετευριστῶν τριῶ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <num value="3"/>. τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αχέως</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οὖν</unclear> μοι 

    <lb n="17"/>γράψον <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να εὐψυχῶ <gap extent="9" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> ἄσπ</supplied>α-

    <lb n="18"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>α<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὴ</unclear>ν ἀγαθὴν Φλο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υρε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="low" reason="lost">ίαν σου</supplied> καὶ 

    <lb n="19"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὰ</supplied> τέκνα σου καὶ Κάνω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ον. ἀσπάζε</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>αί 

    <lb n="20"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σε</unclear> Κύριλλα καὶ τὰ κορά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σια</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="21"/><handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σθα</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ί</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>ε εὔχομαι 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

